      <cite class='section'> Deb 14 August 1843 vol 71 cc688-9</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_688' title='Col. 688 &mdash;  Deb 14 August 1843 vol 71 c688' name='column_688' href='#column_688' rel='bookmark'>688</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S3V0071P0-00929'>
        <a name='S3V0071P0_18430814_HOLR2_8'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-thomas-spring-rice' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S3V0071P0_18430814_HOLR2_8' title='Link to this speech by Mr Thomas Spring-Rice' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
